<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Denno Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9fb;
            color: #172B4D;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9fb;
        }

        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .logo img {
                height: 30px;
            }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #172B4D;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0052CC;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

            .button:hover {
                background-color: #0047B3;
            }

        .description-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: inline;
        }

        .learn-more {
            color: #0052CC;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .learn-more:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .note-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 15px;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .note-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        .note-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .note-content h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .note-content p {
            margin: 5px 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #0052cc;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@Model.Message</h1>

        <p>Join them on Denno to collaborate, manage projects, and reach new productivity peaks.</p>

        <a href="#" class="button">Go to Workspace</a>

        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.Description)) 
        {
            <div class="note-container">
                <img src="@(Model.SenderAvatar ?? "")" alt="Avatar" class="note-avatar">
                <div class="note-content">
                    <h3>A note from @Model.SenderName</h3>
                    <p>Hey, join us</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        }

        <p><span class="description-title">What is Denno?</span> Imagine a white board, filled with lists of sticky notes, with each note as a task. Now imagine that each of those sticky notes has photos, attachments from other data sources like Jira or Salesforce, documents, due dates, and more.</p>

        <p>Now imagine that you can take that whiteboard anywhere you go on your smartphone, and can access it from any computer through the web. That's Denno! <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn more</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>